modName: Guy Fawkes Mask V for Vendetta Resource
summary: A Blender file consisted of two Guy Fawkes mask, 1 high poly and 1 low. For modders who have the ability to make use of them.
descriptionHtml:
[I did not make this!!! All credit goes to \'Jimmyon\']
I found this Guy Fawkes mask online that\'s very well done, especially the high poly one. I\'m just wondering if any pro modders out there can turn this into a usable mask for Skyrim.
This is originally made for Blender, not 3DSMAX
Please feel free to abuse this however you like, just make sure to saying it was Jimmyon who made this. NOT ME
author: Jimmyon
